Message:
-- AdminCommands Script
    local Players = game:GetService("Players")
    local Commands = require(script.Commands)
    local Config = require(script.Config)

    Players.PlayerAdded:Connect(function(player)
        player.Chatted:Connect(function(message)
            -- Check if the message starts with the admin prefix
            if message:sub(1, #Config.Prefix) == Config.Prefix then
                local commandString = message:sub(#Config.Prefix + 1)
                local args = string.split(commandString, " ")
                local commandName = table.remove(args, 1):lower()

                -- Check if the player is an admin
                if table.find(Config.Admins, player.Name) or table.find(Config.Admins, player.UserId) then
                    -- Check if the command exists in the Commands module
                    if Commands[commandName] then
                        Commands[commandName](player, args) -- Call the command function
                    else
                        -- Command not found feedback
                    end
                else
                    -- Not an admin feedback
                end
            end
        end)
    end)
